description: Alan Moore and David Lloyd's powerful epic about loss of freedom and individuality gets the Absolute treatment for the first time in this new, oversized slipcase edition! Taking place in a totalitarian England following a devastating war that changed the face of the planet, V FOR VENDETTA was the inspiration for the hit 2005 movie starring Natalie Portman and Hugo Weaving. This amazing graphic novel spotlights a mysterious man in a white porcelain mask and his young protégé as they fight political oppressors through terrorism and seemingly absurd acts. It's a gripping tale of the blurred lines between ideological good and evil and details a world where political and personal freedoms are non-existent. This new edition features the improved production values and coloring from the 2005 hardcover in larger format for optimum enjoyment of the stunning art and story that the Portland Mercury called, "Perhaps Moore's most powerful work."
name: HC

description: In one of the last missions of the original team, a vital device, capable of controlling a deadly space-laser is on the move. Can the Joes accomplish their mission? Can they even trust their commanders?

description: This Issue The G.I.Joe flash back story continues! As the Joes attempt one FINAL mission to deliver a top secret weapon in Downtown Manhattan, DESTRO arrives to stop them. Cobra wants the new technology the Joes have, and will stop at nothing to get it!
name: The Mission That Never Was part 2 of 4:Two If By Sea

description: With the McGuffin device now in the hands of Cobra, G.I.Joe must attack Destro's Castle head on to retrieve it! Snake-Eyes, Duke, Scarlett, Stalker, and the gang face off against Destro, Baroness, Cobra Commander, Billy, and Dr. Mindbender. Even worse, the Jugglers refuse to answer any Joe pleas for help.
name: The Mission That Never Was part 3 of 4:Assault On The Silent Castle

description: A running firefight through Destro's personal castle leads to crosses and double crosses. Worse, the Joes' transport home has exploded.
name: The Mission That Never Was part 4 of 4

description: Duke leads a Joe team to investigate a scientific installation. Only problem is, last time he led a team in this very place, he was the only survivor.
name: Icebound part 1

description: "Icebound" Part two, Trapped inside an isolated arctic base, Duke, Snake Eyes, Scarlett, Frostbite, Lifeline and Airtight not only realize they're not alone, but also begin to understand the nature of the savage, genetically-corrupted creatures haunting the base's corridors. And just when they thought it couldn't get any weirder, a threat previously frozen starts to thaw... The sub-zero thrills continue in G.I. Joe: Icebound.
name: Icebound part 2

description: The team is seperated deep in the Arctic base. Humanoid beasts are on the rampage and their very touch could mean death.
name: Icebound part 3

description: Duke tries to save his team and innocent bystander from a rampaging horde of humanoid beasts. But it might be too late for any of them...
name: Icebound part 4

description: A new era for the DC Universe begins here! When a city filled with alien super-beings crash-lands in California, only the World's Greatest Super-Heroes can hope to contain the damage. Struggling to control their path across hundreds of miles of cities and towns, where can the combined heroes of Earth and Haven find a safe place for the space-born city to stop its incredible journey?
name: Arrival
